title: 08/19/2021 DPS Hour 1 Is Aaron Rodgers Done in Green Bay After This Year?
itunes:title: 08/19/2021 DPS Hour 1 Is Aaron Rodgers Done in Green Bay After This Year?
description:
Jonas Knox, Brady Quinn and LaVar Arrington, in for Dan, debate whether or not Aaron Rodgers is done in Green Bay after this season after saying he doesn't want this to be a "farewell tour." The QB battle between Cam Newton and Mac Jones will be on display tonight between the Pats and Eagles. Plus, the divas Kevin Durant and Draymond Green continue to talk about their breakup years later.
